    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiſſi Landis/\nkaſ Wahrtis bija ar teem Wez-\nzajeem: Mehs effam Leezinceeki:\nLai tas KUNGS fcho Geewu/\nkaſ tawa Namina nahk/ darra\nka Raëli un Leü/ kaſ abbi Isra-\neka Namunu irr watrojutchas/\nun ſtiprina tew eekſch Eewrataß/\nun darra tew Slawu eekſch Bet-\nlemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un taws Namslai irr/ ka\nPeereza Nams/fo TahmareJuh-\ndam irr dsemdejſi/ no ta Dsim-\nmuma/ fo tas KUNGS tew\ndohs no ſchihs jaunas Geewas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nehme Boasto Rut-\nti/ un ta bija winnam par Gee-\nwu/ un wiꞥſch gahje pee tahs/\nun tas KUNGS deive winnai/\nka ta genuhta tappe/ un weenn\nDehlu dseindeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tahs Geewas\nus Naëmju: Swehtihts lat irr\ntas KUNGS/ kaſ tew ne irr liʒ-\nzis truhkt weenu Tuwu.Raddu\nfchodeen/ un winna Wahrtis lai\ntohp flawejaṁs eekſch Israëta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas buhs jums par At-\nſpirdsinaschanu tahs Diwehſeles/\nun par Uſturretchanit tawa\nWezzuna/ jo tawa Weddekle/\nfo tu mihto/ irr winnu dsemdejſi/\nkaſ tew labbaki irr ne ka feptin\nDehli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Naëmja nehme to\nBehrnizu/ un likte to faua Kleh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs Kaïnimnas dew\nwinnam Wahrtu/ fazzidainas\nTai Naëmjaï irr Dehls dsimmis,\nun tee nofauze winna Wahrt\nObed/ ſchis irr Jsaja Dahwid\nTehwa/ Tehws:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee nu irr Peereza Au\nguni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peerez dsemdinaja Ezro\nnu/ un Ezrons dsemdinaja Ram\nimu/ un Rams dsemdinaja Am\nminadabu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Amminadabs dsemdi\nnaja Naëffonu / un Naëffon\ndsemdinaja Salmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Salmus dsemdinaja Bo\nafu/ un Boas dsemdinaja Obedu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Obeds dsemdinaja Iſaſu / un Iſajus dsemdinaja\nDahwidu.\n"
    }
  ],
